---
title: Let's start using Misskey
description: Misskey is a forever evolving, sophisticated microblogging platform. ―― Why not leave the turmoil of cities for a while and dive into the new network?
styleRequires: ["top"]
---
#toppage
  section#top.loadts
    .texts
      .slogan.h4.font-weight-light.loadts.scrollts-fadeInLeftBig.scrollts-e-2.scrollts-u-5.scrollts-nomargin Connect to the new world
      h1.font-weight-light.loadts.scrollts-fadeInLeftBig.scrollts-e-2.scrollts-u-5.scrollts-nomargin Let's start using Misskey
      p.loadts.scrollts-fadeInLeftBig.scrollts-e-4.scrollts-u-5.scrollts-nomargin Misskey is a forever evolving, sophisticated microblogging platform.
    .scnshts
      +picture({src:"/files/images/imports/2020/03/desktop-2.png", alt:"Desktop", class:"loadts scrollts-e-1 scrollts-nomargin raise-1", sizes: "(max-width: 575.98px) 120vw, (max-width: 1199.98px) 80vw, 60vw"})
      +picture({src:"/files/images/imports/2020/05/scnsht-mobile-2.png", alt:"Mobile", class:"loadts scrollts-e-1 scrollts-nomargin raise-1", sizes: "(max-width: 575.98px) 60vw, 20vw"})
      img(src="/files/images/imports/2019/03/ai_svg.svg" alt="Ai").loadts.scrollts-fadeIn.scrollts-e-3.scrollts-nomargin
      div.small.loadts.scrollts-fadeIn.scrollts-e-3.scrollts-nomargin Ai, the mascot of Misskey
  section#section_1.bg-primary.text-white: .container
    p.text-center Thank you for finding Misskey! Misskey is a #[span.font-weight-bold distributed microblogging] from Earth. Misskey and other SNS connect with each other through the Fediverse (a universe composed of various SNS).
    p.text-center Why not leave the turmoil of cities for a while and dive into the new network?
    p.mt-1.text-center
      a(href="#s3anc").btn.btn-lg.btn-light.text-primary.mr-2.scrollts.scrollts-flipInX.scrollts-nomargin Start
      a(href="wiki/questions").btn.btn-lg.btn-outline-light.mr-2.scrollts.scrollts-flipInX.scrollts-nomargin FAQ
      a(href="wiki/developers").btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.scrollts.scrollts-flipInX.scrollts-nomargin Run
  .text-center
    +ad({ class: "aitaso", slot: "4149683131", format: "horizontal", allowFullWidth: "true" })
  section#section_2.bg-white: .container
    h2.text-center.mt-3 Reasons to start using Misskey
    p.text-center There are many reasons to choose Misskey as everyday SNS.

    section.s2-item
      h3.text-center Many features
      p.text-center Abilities of Misskey
      p.text-center
        a(href="wiki/").btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.scrollts.scrollts-jackInTheBox
          +fa_fw('book')
          | See usage in wiki

      .row.mt-45
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('comment-alt', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Flexible posting functionality
                p.mb-0
                  +fa_fw('i-cursor')
                  | #[b Freely configurable character limit] for each individual instance
                p.mb-0
                  +fa_fw('unlock')
                  |  You can #[b configure the privacy] of your posts finely
                p.mb-0
                  +fa_fw('eye-slash')
                  |  You can #[b hide] your improper messages or images
            a(href="wiki/usage/post").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About posting Notes
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('edit', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Text formatting
                p.mb-0 Let's decorate your notes and profile! Formatting via Misskey Flavored Markdown (MFM) is available.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/03/mfm.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
            a(href="wiki/usage/mfm").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About MFM
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('surprise', 'far')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Reactions
                p.mb-0 Easily express empathy for notes. You can select emojis and send a reaction to a note.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/03/reaction-2.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('chart-pie', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Polls
                p.mb-0 Ask everyone for their opinions. You can create a questionnaire with up to 10 choices. Multiple answers can be accepted and an expiration date can be set.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/03/vote.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('cloud', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Drive
                p.mb-0 Save files and share them many times. You can manage attached files with Drive, or upload files to Drive beforehand.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/11/drive.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
            a(href="wiki/usage/drive").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About Drive
        //- article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('gamepad', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Gaming
                p.mb-0
                  | Let's play together! You can battle with other users.
                  br
                  | In Reversi, users' icon show as stones and you can play with #[a(href="https://github.com/syuilo/misskey/issues/1200" target="_blank" rel="noopener") customed rule].
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/03/reversi.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('comments', 'far')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Messaging
                p.mb-0
                  | Let's chat.
                  br
                  | You can chat one-on-one or in a group on a dedicated screen.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/10/talk.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
            a(href="wiki/usage/messaging").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About Messaging
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('sticky-note', 'far')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Pages
                p.mb-0
                  | Make a "generator" or write a sentence.
                  br
                  | In pages, you can place blocks such as text and sections or create a simple program.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/10/page.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
            a(href="wiki/usage/pages").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About Pages
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('satellite')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Antennas
                p.mb-0
                  | Search for notes about yourself
                  br
                  | Collect notes that fulfill freely configurable conditions via Antennas
        article.col-12.col-md-6.col-xl-4
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('door-open', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Rooms
                p.mb-0
                  | Arrange various furniture and make your own room.
                  br
                  | The room you create can be shared with everyone by URL.
            +picture({src: "/files/images/imports/2019/10/room.png", loading: "lazy", sizes: "calc(100vw - 1rem), (min-width: 576px) 524px, (min-width: 768px) 344px, (min-width: 992px) 464px, (min-width: 1200px) 364px"})
            a(href="wiki/usage/rooms").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About Rooms

    hr#section_2_b

    section.s2-item
      h3.text-center Customizable Interface
      p.text-center You can customize the web client at will.

      .row.mt-45
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('calculator', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Widgets
                p.mb-0 A small widget displays various information. You can arrange the widgets freely.
            //- img(src="/files/images/imports/2019/03/widgets.svg")
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('palette', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Themes
                p.mb-0
                  | You can freely change the background color, text, border color, etc.
                  br
                  | Created themes can be saved and shared as a file.
            a(href="https://assets.msky.cafe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold Assets Store

    hr#section_2_a

    section.s2-item
      h3.text-center Independence and Sociality
      p.text-center Choose an instance that you like or manage your own.

      .row.mt-45
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('globe', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Fediverse
                p.mb-0
                  | Since Misskey uses a server-to-server communication protocol called ActivityPub,
                  | you can follow users from different instances and #[a(href="https://fediverse.gitlab.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener") other services], where you can see and react to notes.
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .s2-card-icon.fa-2x: +fa_fw('server', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 Easy server setup
                p.mb-0 Installing Misskey is easy, so running your own SNS is possible.
            a(href="wiki/developers/").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold About instance setup and maintenance

    hr#section_2_c

    section.s2-item.pb-0
      h3.text-center Open source
      p.text-center Misskey is open source software. Anyone can participate in its development and translation. You can also fork the repository and add your own extensions.
      p.text-center
        a(href="https://github.com/syuilo/misskey" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-lg.btn-dark.mr-2.scrollts.scrollts-zoomIn
          +fa_fw('github', 'fab')
          | GitHub
        a(href="https://crowdin.com/project/misskey" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-lg.btn-warning.scrollts.scrollts-zoomIn
          | Crowdin (to translate)

      .row.mt-45
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .font-size-16: +fa_fw('code', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 API
                p.mb-0 Make your apps and clients to make your life better. You can use almost all features of Misskey in your apps. Play against the reversi bot and let everyone know what you are listening to!
            a(href="wiki/developers/api").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold API Usage
        article.col-12.col-md-6
          .card.scrollts.scrollts-fadeInLeftSmall
            .s2-card-grid
              .font-size-16: +fa_fw('balance-scale', 'fas')
              .s2-card-text
                h4 AGPL v3
                p.mb-0 Misskey is licensed under GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL v3).
            a(href="wiki/developers/modifying-code-and-license").s2-card-link.font-weight-bold License

  .text-center#s3anc
    +ad({ class: "aitaso", slot: "4149683131", format: "horizontal", allowFullWidth: "true" })

  section#section_3.bg-dark.text-white: .container
    h2.text-center Getting started
    p.text-center Register your account at any instance that you like!
    p.text-center You can talk to users from other instances. The instance URL is part of your ID.
    hr.my-4
    h3#instances List of recommended instances
    +instancesList('selected', ['light', 'white-50', 'dark', 'dark'], 'fadeInUp')
    p.text-center.my-2
      a(href="./wiki/instances/").scrollts-nomargin.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm See more...

    p.text-white-50.pt-2 We are always adding new instances. If you want us to add any to the list, please send a Note to @joinmisskey@misskey.io.

  section#section_6.bg-white: .container.text-center.text-dark
    h2 Misskey has been featured in internet news! (in japanese only)
    p.m-0.text-center
      a(href="http://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/1804/17/news124.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="ActivityPub対応国産SNS「Misskey」、LTLも実装 ―― ITmedia NEWS").p-1.mr-2
        img(src="/files/images/imports/2018/07/ITmediaNEWS.png" style="height: 33px" alt="ITmedia NEWS" loading="lazy")
      a(href="https://www.moongift.jp/2018/07/misskey-%e5%88%86%e6%95%a3%e5%9e%8b%e3%83%9e%e3%82%a4%e3%82%af%e3%83%ad%e3%83%96%e3%83%ad%e3%82%b0%e3%82%b5%e3%83%bc%e3%83%93%e3%82%b9/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Misskey - 分散型マイクロブログサービス ―― MOONGIFT").p-1
        img(src="/files/images/imports/2018/07/MOONGIFT.png" style="height: 33px" alt="MOONGIFT" loading="lazy")

  section#section_6_1.bg-white: .container.text-center.text-dark
    h2 Statistics
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-md-4.mt-2
        .font-weight-bold Total user count
        .h1=numeral(stats.usersCount).format('0,0')
      .col-md-4.mt-2
        .font-weight-bold Total note count
        .h1=numeral(stats.notesCount).format('0,0')
      .col-md-4.mt-2
        .font-weight-bold Total instance count
        .h1=numeral(stats.instancesCount).format('0,0')
    p.mb-0.mt-3.text-muted.small The above is the sum of values from all listed instances, gathered at the following date: #{updateMoment.tz('Asia/Tokyo').format('lll z')}

  section#section_7: .container
    h2.text-center Supporters
    p.text-center
      a(href="credit#patrons").btn.btn-lg.btn-light.text-primary.mr-2
        | List of sponsers
      a(href="https://github.com/syuilo/misskey/blob/master/docs/DONATORS.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-lg.btn-light.text-primary
        | List of donators

    hr.my-4
    h3.text-center Support Misskey
    p.text-center
      | Do you like Misskey? Misskey is developed by individuals. It's free and open-source.
      br
      | Misskey does not show advertisements so the user experience is not harmed, but considerable development costs still exist.
      br
      | Please support the development of Misskey.
    a(href="https://www.patreon.com/syuilo" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-outline-primary.mb-2
      +fa_fw('patreon', 'fab')
      | Becoming a Patron
    a(href="http://amzn.asia/7O1LEI5" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-outline-primary.mb-2
      +fa_fw('amazon', 'fab')
      | Wishlist
    a(href="https://www.bountysource.com/teams/misskey" target="_blank" rel="noopener").btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-outline-primary.mb-2
      | Bountysource
    p.text-center ... or #[a(href="https://misskey.io/@syuilo" target="_blank" rel="noopener") contact the developer]
    p.text-center
      a(href="wiki/about-jm").btn.btn-primary.btn-lg Support joinmisskey

  section#section_4.bg-success: .container.text-white
    .row
      .col-12.col-md-6
        .py-3
          a(href="blog/").btn.btn-lg.btn-outline-light
            +fa("broadcast-tower")
            |  Blog
          p.mt-1.mb-0.p-0 Notifications for release notes of new Misskey versions
      .col-12.col-md-6.scrollts-e-1
        .py-3
          a(href="credit").btn.btn-lg.btn-outline-light
            +fa("users")
            |  Credits
          p.mt-1.mb-0.p-0 People who contribute to Misskey's development
